Feature: Job Application Portal
  As a job seeker
  I want to navigate the job application portal
  So that I can view and apply for job positions

  Background:
    Given I am on the job app home page

  @smoke @navigation
  Scenario: View job application homepage
    Then I should see "Login" link
    And I should see "Register" link
    And I should see the navigation bar

  @smoke @authentication
  Scenario: Navigate to login page
    When I click on "Login" link
    Then I should see the login form
    And I should see "Email" input field
    And I should see "Password" input field
    And I should see "Login" button

  @smoke @authentication
  Scenario: Navigate to registration page
    When I click on "Register" link
    Then I should see the registration form
    And I should see "Email" input field
    And I should see "Password" input field
    And I should see "Create Account" button

  @negative @validation
  Scenario: Login with empty email
    When I click on "Login" link
    And I enter password "TestPassword123"
    And I click the login button
    Then I should see an error message about email

  @negative @validation
  Scenario: Login with empty password
    When I click on "Login" link
    And I enter email "test@example.com"
    And I click the login button
    Then I should see an error message about password

  @ui @responsive
  Scenario: Check page has essential elements
    Then I should see a header element
    And I should see a footer element
    And I should see a navigation menu
